description: ChinaAMC NASDAQ 100 ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by BMO Global Asset Management (Asia) Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors, excluding financial sector. The fund invests in the stocks of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the NASDAQ-100 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. ChinaAMC NASDAQ 100 ETF was formed on February 11, 2016 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: ChinaAMC NASDAQ 100 ETF
